pf.graph
Interface Path

All Superinterfaces:
java.lang.Iterable<Edge>
All Known Implementing Classes:
PathImpl
public interface Path
extends java.lang.Iterable<Edge>

Path stores a chain of edges. Each edge shares a vertex with the next one. It can iterate over edges and vertices.

Author:
Adam Juraszek

verticesIterator

java.util.Iterator<Vertex> verticesIterator()
